{"tid":2307202,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港娛樂圈崩壞史]呢班巨星真係死得好合時","createTime":"2020-12-01T04:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T07:12:36.000Z","uid":33259,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e27f3ced8c8b944568941d6ad9851455507dea18","tid":2307202,"uid":33259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:37:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n以前嘅巨星真係可以好紅，Danny仔/哥哥/梅姐<br />\n紅遍東南亞，以至日韓，影響力無與倫比<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z5TSB8w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz5TSB8w.jpg&h=00a274b2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rJbQoOC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrJbQoOC.jpg&h=22e192eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身極具港英殖民地時代既中西文化特色<br />\n個種風韻同品味簡直係一時無兩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦都代表經得起時代洗禮嘅巨星喺有底韻同信念<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而佢哋離世留住咗佢哋形象最好既時刻 (當年振災酬款，發起64集會等)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oqpymwS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoqpymwS.jpg&h=22c2127d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但睇返曾經萬世曯目嘅廢老護旗「明星」<br />\n奶既奶，變質既變質<br />\n一堆無個人特色既藝人只會被淘汰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jUvd5ZU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjUvd5ZU.jpg&h=40ebdb90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTVB個堆亦根本唔會有突圍而出嘅機會<br />\n呢個百花齊放嘅影視時代，Youtube/Netflix/Patron etc.<br />\n主流媒體生存空間愈嚟愈細，連八卦新聞都無咗吸引力，帶唔起話題<br />\n時代已變，觀眾群已經時代洗禮<br />\n覺醒咗好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[url]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94EOar4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94EOar4.jpg&h=9b797cc6&s={SIZE}\" />[/url]<br />\nnewsfeed愈嚟愈失去效果，大家對AI演算法愈嚟愈敏感<br />\n以前連content farm都大把人share，而家只要五毛PR一出現<br />\n大家警覺性已經好高，但同時亦鬥黃嚴重咗<br />\n以前跟Script可以塑造到明星形象包裝<br />\n而家基本上問你個人取態已經暴露無遺<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zGj6Gzk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzGj6Gzk.jpg&h=3bc8a6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資訊太多太快，要catch attention已經唔容易<br />\n試問，無質素嘅藝人仲可以點生存<br />\n事實亦都真係睇唔到香港點樣再「全民造星」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP.S. 大包圍，乜都鳩噏下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c342fa85d79c7fddb080cf88385d3973f3d3558","tid":2307202,"uid":80814,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"諗起以前曾志偉嗰班偽人成日話好愛香港，想用自己影響力為香港做啲嘢嗰陣，就想嘔"},{"pid":"d5008978995da71ca007aac86f60d4e09d875b1a","tid":2307202,"uid":33259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5c342fa85d79c7fddb080cf88385d3973f3d3558","tid":2307202,"uid":80814,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"諗起以前曾志偉嗰班偽人成日話好愛香港，想用自己影響力為香港做啲嘢嗰陣，就想嘔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T05:10:39.000Z","msg":"香港演藝人協會俱樂部化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13195be45c2461d074ed2d3aeb62622eb67a0672","tid":2307202,"uid":28068,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T05:47:55.000Z","msg":"所謂蓋棺定論啦<br />\n當然你可以嘗試猜測如果佢地無死會有咩立場<br />\n但對於死左既人既評價<br />\n始終以佢在生時所做既野黎定論會好d"},{"pid":"80e848e5de2a92289f8588d4c7ae48309dd03340","tid":2307202,"uid":33259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"13195be45c2461d074ed2d3aeb62622eb67a0672","tid":2307202,"uid":28068,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T05:47:55.000Z","msg":"所謂蓋棺定論啦<br />\n當然你可以嘗試猜測如果佢地無死會有咩立場<br />\n但對於死左既人既評價<br />\n始終以佢在生時所做既野黎定論會好d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T07:12:36.000Z","msg":"的確係。<br />\n事實證明一粒巨星，不需要有太長久光芒。"}]}